            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "One would think that buying an almost-new vehicle from a dealership would be reassurance enough you’re not getting something that’s been stolen, but according to a shocking report from Detroit Free Press, that’s not necessarily the case these days. The paper found a pipeline of Ford F-150s stolen from ",
